---
title: Smoky Paprika Chicken with White Beans plus Carrots, Zucchini & Lemony Yogurt Sauce
description: In this wholesome bowl inspired by Spanish cuisine, you’ll find a delightful variety of textures, colors, and flavors. Juicy seared chicken seasoned with smoked paprika is served over saucy stewed white beans with beautifully browned roasted carrots and zucchini. You’ll drizzle it all with a bright lemon yogurt sauce and garnish with zippy scallion greens for a delicious meal that hits all the right notes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/656f8a5fddd2bdfd232c7674-a86ceba8.jpeg
